sources.title: Martin Luther
sources.description: See more at IMDb; http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0046051/ Stars: Niall MacGinnis, John Ruddock and Pierre Lefevre In the opening narration, approx 2 minutes, there are several very poor audio edits. Also, the overall background noise level stands out a little more than usual. Both problems are inherent in the source.
